<div class="m-t-xl m-b clearfix animated fadeInLeft">

    <span class="h3 font-thin purple">What does a winning entry look like? Tips to get you started</span>
    <hr />
    <div class="clear">
        <ol>
            <li class="margin-bottom-10"><span class="purple">Be creative –</span><br />the more creative the better. Push the boundaries and let your imagination run wild in terms of how you deliver your entry</li>
            <li class="margin-bottom-10"><span class="text-primary">Quality not quantity -</span><br /> You won’t get more points for the more values you demonstrate or the longer the list of things you do to demonstrate a value, it’s about the quality of what you do even if it’s something small</li>
            <li class="margin-bottom-10"><span class="text-success">It’s all about impact –</span><br /> don’t just tell us what you do, tell us about how you do it and the impact it has on the customer or your colleagues </li>
            <li class="margin-bottom-10">
                <span class="text-info">Keep it simple –</span><br />
                be concise, keep it short and sweet. Why not have a look at the
                @if (ViewBag.NetworkPC)
                {
                    <a href="http://intranet.aib.pri/intranet/toneofvoice.nsf/site?openframeset" target="_blank" class="text-info"></a>
                }
                else
                {
                    <span>AIB tone of voice intranet page</span>
                }
                to get some tips
            </li>
            <li class="margin-bottom-10"><span class="text-warning">Inspire –</span><br /> we want your entries to inspire others to live the values so think about what other colleagues can take from your entry</li>
        </ol>



    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="hidden-desktop">
        <a class="btn btn-default" href="#content">Top of page</a>
    </div>


</div>
